::Prowl::

Prowl looks from the table to Dinobot as they aproach the repair station, 
realizing Dinobot would not be easy to lift up to there. He looks to Iron 
Raptor, his optics melting into a look of love. He shakes his head to get his 
thoughts back together, remembering that Dinobot's life depended on the speed 
of the procedure.

"Let's get him onto the table," he says, straining to lift his side of 
Dinobot.
